### Fetch all books
GET {{host}}/books
Accept: application/json

### Get book by id
GET {{host}}/books/1
Accept: application/json

### Create new book
POST {{host}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hello world",
  "author": "Someone"
}

### Update a book
PUT {{host}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "What a new title",
  "author": "Nobody"
}

### Delete a book
DELETE {{host}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 2
}
